# Repo-owned, upgrade-proof ignore (devkit manages only the root .gitignore).
#
# dist/index.js is the committed ncc bundle action.yml runs; dist/package.json
# is ncc's module-type marker. Everything else here is tsc/ncc byproduct:
# tsconfig.json sets outDir ./dist with declaration + declarationMap, so
# `just build`/`just bundle` emit dist/src/*.d.ts(.map). Those .d.ts.map files
# embed absolute file:// paths and so differ per checkout location; keep them
# untracked so the whole-tree Dist Check (git status on dist/) stays clean
# (#70). The root .gitignore's language-aware Node fragment deliberately drops
# the blanket dist/ ignore (#1024), so this lives here instead.
/src/
